# Hotel Search API Integration (PHP)

## Overview

This project is a clean and professional PHP integration with the Booking.com Hotels API (via RapidAPI). It fetches hotel data for a given destination and date range, applies pricing logic, and prepares frontend-ready output.

---

## Key Highlights

* Clean, readable PHP code with proper naming and indentation
* Error handling for API failures and empty responses
* Safe price calculations with 2-decimal formatting
* 15% business markup applied to total and per-night prices
* Debug-friendly output using `print_r()` during development

---

## Tech Stack

* PHP (Core)
* Booking.com API (RapidAPI)
* cURL

---

## Professional Practices Used

* Graceful handling of cURL and API errors
* Type-safe price calculations using floats
* Clear separation of configuration, logic, and output
* Credentials kept configurable (inlined only for testing)

---

## Usage

* Development: View full data using `print_r()`
* Production: Easily switch to `json_encode()` output

